<h1>Online Bible: New World Translation of the Holy Scriptures</h1>
</noscript>
<p class="title">1 Chronicles 3:1-24</p>
<form class="formtext">
<input type="hidden" name="chapterCount" value="29">
<input type="hidden" name="verseCount" value="24">
<p><a name="bk1" class="vsAnchor">1</a>
       <span id="vs1">And these became the sons of David that were born to him in He&acute;bron: the firstborn Am&acute;non, of A&middot;hin&acute;o&middot;am the Jez&acute;re&middot;el&middot;i&middot;tess, the second, Daniel, of Ab&acute;i&middot;gail the Car&acute;mel&middot;it&middot;ess,</span> <a name="bk2" class="vsAnchor">2</a>
       <span id="vs2">the third, Ab&acute;sa&middot;lom the son of Ma&acute;a&middot;cah the daughter of Tal&acute;mai the king of Gesh&acute;ur, the fourth, Ad&middot;o&middot;ni&acute;jah the son of Hag&acute;gith,</span> <a name="bk3" class="vsAnchor">3</a>
       <span id="vs3">the fifth, Sheph&middot;a&middot;ti&acute;ah, of A&middot;bi&acute;tal, the sixth, Ith&acute;re&middot;am, of Eg&acute;lah his wife.</span> <a name="bk4" class="vsAnchor">4</a>
       <span id="vs4">There were six born to him in He&acute;bron; and he continued to reign there seven years and six months, and for thirty-three years he reigned in Jerusalem.</span>
</p>

<p><a name="bk5" class="vsAnchor">5</a>
       <span id="vs5">And there were these born to him in Jerusalem: Shim&acute;e&middot;a and Sho&acute;bab and Nathan and Sol&acute;o&middot;mon, four of Bath-she&acute;ba the daughter of Am&acute;mi&middot;el,</span> <a name="bk6" class="vsAnchor">6</a>
       <span id="vs6">and Ib&acute;har and E&middot;lish&acute;a&middot;ma and E&middot;liph&acute;e&middot;let,</span> <a name="bk7" class="vsAnchor">7</a>
       <span id="vs7">and No&acute;gah and Ne&acute;pheg and Ja&middot;phi&acute;a,</span> <a name="bk8" class="vsAnchor">8</a>
       <span id="vs8">and E&middot;lish&acute;a&middot;ma and E&middot;li&acute;a&middot;da and E&middot;liph&acute;e&middot;let, nine,</span> <a name="bk9" class="vsAnchor">9</a>
       <span id="vs9">all the sons of David besides the sons of the concubines, and Ta&acute;mar their sister.</span>
</p>

<p><a name="bk10" class="vsAnchor">10</a>
       <span id="vs10">And the son of Sol&acute;o&middot;mon was Re&middot;ho&middot;bo&acute;am, A&middot;bi&acute;jah his son, A&acute;sa his son, Je&middot;hosh&acute;a&middot;phat his son,</span> <a name="bk11" class="vsAnchor">11</a>
       <span id="vs11">Je&middot;ho&acute;ram his son, A&middot;ha&middot;zi&acute;ah his son, Je&middot;ho&acute;ash his son,</span> <a name="bk12" class="vsAnchor">12</a>
       <span id="vs12">Am&middot;a&middot;zi&acute;ah his son, Az&middot;a&middot;ri&acute;ah his son, Jo&acute;tham his son,</span> <a name="bk13" class="vsAnchor">13</a>
       <span id="vs13">A&acute;haz his son, Hez&middot;e&middot;ki&acute;ah his son, Ma&middot;nas&acute;seh his son,</span> <a name="bk14" class="vsAnchor">14</a>
       <span id="vs14">A&acute;mon his son, Jo&middot;si&acute;ah his son.</span> <a name="bk15" class="vsAnchor">15</a>
       <span id="vs15">And the sons of Jo&middot;si&acute;ah were the firstborn Jo&middot;ha&acute;nan, the second, Je&middot;hoi&acute;a&middot;kim, the third, Zed&middot;e&middot;ki&acute;ah, the fourth, Shal&acute;lum.</span> <a name="bk16" class="vsAnchor">16</a>
       <span id="vs16">And the sons of Je&middot;hoi&acute;a&middot;kim were Jec&middot;o&middot;ni&acute;ah his son, Zed&middot;e&middot;ki&acute;ah his son.</span> <a name="bk17" class="vsAnchor">17</a>
       <span id="vs17">And the sons of Jec&middot;o&middot;ni&acute;ah as prisoner were She&middot;al&acute;ti&middot;el his son</span> <a name="bk18" class="vsAnchor">18</a>
       <span id="vs18">and Mal&middot;chi&acute;ram and Pe&middot;dai&acute;ah and She&middot;naz&acute;zar, Jek&middot;a&middot;mi&acute;ah, Hosh&acute;a&middot;ma and Ned&middot;a&middot;bi&acute;ah.</span> <a name="bk19" class="vsAnchor">19</a>
       <span id="vs19">And the sons of Pe&middot;dai&acute;ah were Ze&middot;rub&acute;ba&middot;bel and Shim&acute;e&middot;i; and the sons of Ze&middot;rub&acute;ba&middot;bel were Me&middot;shul&acute;lam and Han&middot;a&middot;ni&acute;ah (and She&middot;lo&acute;mith was their sister);</span> <a name="bk20" class="vsAnchor">20</a>
       <span id="vs20">and Ha&middot;shu&acute;bah and O&acute;hel and Ber&middot;e&middot;chi&acute;ah and Has&middot;a&middot;di&acute;ah, Ju&acute;shab-he&acute;sed, five.</span> <a name="bk21" class="vsAnchor">21</a>
       <span id="vs21">And the sons of Han&middot;a&middot;ni&acute;ah were Pel&middot;a&middot;ti&acute;ah and Je&middot;sha&acute;iah, the sons of [Je&middot;sha&acute;iah] Re&middot;pha&acute;iah, the sons of [Re&middot;pha&acute;iah] Ar&acute;nan, the sons of [Ar&acute;nan] O&middot;ba&middot;di&acute;ah, the sons of [O&middot;ba&middot;di&acute;ah] Shec&middot;a&middot;ni&acute;ah;</span> <a name="bk22" class="vsAnchor">22</a>
       <span id="vs22">and the sons of Shec&middot;a&middot;ni&acute;ah, She&middot;mai&acute;ah, and the sons of She&middot;mai&acute;ah, Hat&acute;tush and I&acute;gal and Ba&middot;ri&acute;ah and Ne&middot;a&middot;ri&acute;ah and Sha&acute;phat, six.</span> <a name="bk23" class="vsAnchor">23</a>
       <span id="vs23">And the sons of Ne&middot;a&middot;ri&acute;ah were Eli&middot;o&middot;e&acute;nai and Hiz&middot;ki&acute;ah and Az&middot;ri&acute;kam, three.</span> <a name="bk24" class="vsAnchor">24</a>
       <span id="vs24">And the sons of Eli&middot;o&middot;e&acute;nai were Hod&middot;a&middot;vi&acute;ah and E&middot;li&acute;a&middot;shib and Pe&middot;la&acute;iah and Ak&acute;kub and Jo&middot;ha&acute;nan and De&middot;la&acute;iah and A&middot;na&acute;ni, seven.</span>
</p>
</form>

<script language="JavaScript1.2" type="text/javascript">
