<h1>Online Bible: New World Translation of the Holy Scriptures</h1>
</noscript>
<p class="title">1 Chronicles 25:1-31</p>
<form class="formtext">
<input type="hidden" name="chapterCount" value="29">
<input type="hidden" name="verseCount" value="31">
<p><a name="bk1" class="vsAnchor">1</a>
       <span id="vs1">Further, David and the chiefs of the service groups separated for the service some of the sons of A&acute;saph, He&acute;man and Je&middot;du&acute;thun the ones prophesying with the harps, with the stringed instruments and with the cymbals. And from their number the official men for their service came to be.</span> <a name="bk2" class="vsAnchor">2</a>
       <span id="vs2">Of the sons of A&acute;saph, Zac&acute;cur and Joseph and Neth&middot;a&middot;ni&acute;ah and Ash&middot;a&middot;re&acute;lah, the sons of A&acute;saph under the control of A&acute;saph the one prophesying under the control of the king.</span> <a name="bk3" class="vsAnchor">3</a>
       <span id="vs3">Of Je&middot;du&acute;thun: the sons of Je&middot;du&acute;thun, Ged&middot;a&middot;li&acute;ah and Ze&acute;ri and Je&middot;sha&acute;iah, [and Shim&acute;e&middot;i,] Hash&middot;a&middot;bi&acute;ah and Mat&middot;ti&middot;thi&acute;ah, six, under the control of their father Je&middot;du&acute;thun, who was prophesying with the harp for thanking and praising Jehovah.</span> <a name="bk4" class="vsAnchor">4</a>
       <span id="vs4">Of He&acute;man: the sons of He&acute;man, Buk&middot;ki&acute;ah, Mat&middot;ta&middot;ni&acute;ah, Uz&acute;zi&middot;el, Sheb&acute;u&middot;el and Jer&acute;i&middot;moth, Han&middot;a&middot;ni&acute;ah, Ha&middot;na&acute;ni, E&middot;li&acute;a&middot;thah, Gid&middot;dal&acute;ti and Ro&middot;mam&acute;ti-e&acute;zer, Josh&middot;be&middot;kash&acute;ah, Mal&middot;lo&acute;thi, Ho&acute;thir, Ma&middot;ha&acute;zi&middot;oth.</span> <a name="bk5" class="vsAnchor">5</a>
       <span id="vs5">All these were sons of He&acute;man, a visionary of the king in the things of the [true] God to raise up his horn; thus the [true] God proceeded to give He&acute;man fourteen sons and three daughters.</span> <a name="bk6" class="vsAnchor">6</a>
       <span id="vs6">All these were under the control of their father in song at the house of Jehovah, with cymbals, stringed instruments and harps for the service of the house of the [true] God.</span>
</p>

<p> 
       <span id="vs6-2">Under the control of the king were A&acute;saph and Je&middot;du&acute;thun and He&acute;man.</span>
</p>

<p><a name="bk7" class="vsAnchor">7</a>
       <span id="vs7">And the number of them together with their brothers trained in song to Jehovah, all experts, came to be two hundred and eighty-eight.</span> <a name="bk8" class="vsAnchor">8</a>
       <span id="vs8">So they cast lots as to the things to be taken care of, the little being just the same as the great, the expert along with the learner.</span>
</p>

<p><a name="bk9" class="vsAnchor">9</a>
       <span id="vs9">And the lot proceeded to come out: the first belonging to A&acute;saph for Joseph, for Ged&middot;a&middot;li&acute;ah the second (he and his brothers and his sons were twelve);</span> <a name="bk10" class="vsAnchor">10</a>
       <span id="vs10">the third for Zac&acute;cur, his sons and his brothers, twelve;</span> <a name="bk11" class="vsAnchor">11</a>
       <span id="vs11">the fourth for Iz&acute;ri, his sons and his brothers, twelve;</span> <a name="bk12" class="vsAnchor">12</a>
       <span id="vs12">the fifth for Neth&middot;a&middot;ni&acute;ah, his sons and his brothers, twelve;</span> <a name="bk13" class="vsAnchor">13</a>
       <span id="vs13">the sixth for Buk&middot;ki&acute;ah, his sons and his brothers, twelve;</span> <a name="bk14" class="vsAnchor">14</a>
       <span id="vs14">the seventh for Jesh&middot;a&middot;re&acute;lah, his sons and his brothers, twelve;</span> <a name="bk15" class="vsAnchor">15</a>
       <span id="vs15">the eighth for Je&middot;sha&acute;iah, his sons and his brothers, twelve;</span> <a name="bk16" class="vsAnchor">16</a>
       <span id="vs16">the ninth for Mat&middot;ta&middot;ni&acute;ah, his sons and his brothers, twelve;</span> <a name="bk17" class="vsAnchor">17</a>
       <span id="vs17">the tenth for Shim&acute;e&middot;i, his sons and his brothers, twelve;</span> <a name="bk18" class="vsAnchor">18</a>
       <span id="vs18">the eleventh for Az&acute;ar&middot;el, his sons and his brothers, twelve;</span> <a name="bk19" class="vsAnchor">19</a>
       <span id="vs19">the twelfth for Hash&middot;a&middot;bi&acute;ah, his sons and his brothers, twelve;</span> <a name="bk20" class="vsAnchor">20</a>
       <span id="vs20">for the thirteenth, Shu&acute;ba&middot;el, his sons and his brothers, twelve;</span> <a name="bk21" class="vsAnchor">21</a>
       <span id="vs21">for the fourteenth, Mat&middot;ti&middot;thi&acute;ah, his sons and his brothers, twelve;</span> <a name="bk22" class="vsAnchor">22</a>
       <span id="vs22">for the fifteenth, for Jer&acute;e&middot;moth, his sons and his brothers, twelve;</span> <a name="bk23" class="vsAnchor">23</a>
       <span id="vs23">for the sixteenth, for Han&middot;a&middot;ni&acute;ah, his sons and his brothers, twelve;</span> <a name="bk24" class="vsAnchor">24</a>
       <span id="vs24">for the seventeenth, for Josh&middot;be&middot;kash&acute;ah, his sons and his brothers, twelve;</span> <a name="bk25" class="vsAnchor">25</a>
       <span id="vs25">for the eighteenth, for Ha&middot;na&acute;ni, his sons and his brothers, twelve;</span> <a name="bk26" class="vsAnchor">26</a>
       <span id="vs26">for the nineteenth, for Mal&middot;lo&acute;thi, his sons and his brothers, twelve;</span> <a name="bk27" class="vsAnchor">27</a>
       <span id="vs27">for the twentieth, for E&middot;li&acute;a&middot;thah, his sons and his brothers, twelve;</span> <a name="bk28" class="vsAnchor">28</a>
       <span id="vs28">for the twenty-first, for Ho&acute;thir, his sons and his brothers, twelve;</span> <a name="bk29" class="vsAnchor">29</a>
       <span id="vs29">for the twenty-second, for Gid&middot;dal&acute;ti, his sons and his brothers, twelve;</span> <a name="bk30" class="vsAnchor">30</a>
       <span id="vs30">for the twenty-third, for Ma&middot;ha&acute;zi&middot;oth, his sons and his brothers, twelve;</span> <a name="bk31" class="vsAnchor">31</a>
       <span id="vs31">for the twenty-fourth, for Ro&middot;mam&acute;ti-e&acute;zer, his sons and his brothers, twelve.</span>
</p>
</form>

